These are Puzzles for 4x2 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-8-1::.
There are 2 different nationalities: dutch, canadian
There 2 different types of food: broccoli, spinach
There are 2 different favourite colors: apricot, lavender
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: action, sports
1. the person watching action movies is not to the right of the person eating spinach##8
2. the person eating spinach is somewhere to the left of the person who likes apricot##5
3. the dutch is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |
| Nationality      | canadian     | dutch      |
| Food          | spinach | broccoli    |
| Color         | lavender   | apricot |
| Movie-Genre   | action  | sports      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-8-2::.
2 different games are played: mah-jongg, domino
The people have 2 different hobbies: filmmaking, woodworking
The people have 2 different jobs:  librarian, software-developer
There are 2 different nationalities: japanese, russian
1. the person playing domino is on the far right##1
2. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is somewhere to the left of the librarian##5
3. the software-developer is not to the right of the librarian##8
4. the japanese is not the person who's hobby is woodworking##6

.:: Answer ::.
|             |         1          |      2      |
| Game    | mah-jongg        | domino    |
| Hobby       | filmmaking         | woodworking |
| Job         | software-developer | librarian   |
| Nationality   | japanese               | russian  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-8-3::.
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: epic, thriller
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: december, may
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: lily, orchid
2 different pets are kept: cat, ferret
1. the person who growslily is in an odd position##4
2. the person who growsorchid is not to the right of the owner of the ferret##8
3. the person who's birthday is in december is somewhere to the left of the person watching thriller movies##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |
| Movie-Genre   | epic       | thriller |
| Birthday   | december       | may    |
| Flower   | lily | orchid |
| Pet           | cat        | ferret   |

